@page "/solutions/sales"
@layout MarketingLayout

<PageTitle>NavTour for Sales Teams &mdash; NavTour</PageTitle>
<HeadContent>
    <meta name="description" content="NavTour helps sales teams send personalized demo links before every call, so buyers arrive prepped and reps spend less time on feature tours." />
</HeadContent>

<section class="nt-page-hero">
    <div class="nt-container">
        <span class="eyebrow">Solutions &middot; Sales</span>
        <h1>Turn every discovery call into<br /><em>a deal you already won.</em></h1>
        <p class="lead">Send a personalized NavTour before every call. Buyers arrive prepped, reps skip the basics, and your pipeline moves faster.</p>
        <div class="nt-hero-actions">
            <a href="/register" class="btn btn-orange btn-lg">Start free &rarr;</a>
            <a href="/solutions" class="btn btn-outline btn-lg">All use cases</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="nt-frames-section">
    <div class="nt-container">
        <article class="nt-frame-row">
            <div class="nt-frame-copy">
                <div class="num">01<span class="slash">/</span><span class="lbl">Pre-call prep</span></div>
                <h3>Buyers arrive <em>ready</em> &mdash; no more feature-explanation calls.</h3>
                <p>Send a branded NavTour before every discovery call. Buyers self-qualify by watching the relevant workflows, so the meeting starts at strategic fit, not "can you explain what it does?"</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Personalized with <code style="font-family:var(--nt-mono);font-size:0.88em;background:rgba(251,173,72,0.18);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:4px">&#123;&#123;company&#125;&#125;</code> tokens</li>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Per-viewer analytics — see who watched what before the call</li>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Embeds in Outreach, HubSpot sequences, and email</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="nt-frame-visual">
                <span class="nt-frame-cap">Pre-call showcase &middot; personalized</span>
                <div class="nt-frame-img">
                    <img src="/images/shots/player-step1.png" alt="Personalized demo walkthrough" class="nt-lightbox" />
                </div>
                <div class="anno tl">
                    <div class="lbl">Intent signal</div>
                    <strong>2.4&times; more qualified calls</strong>
                    <p>Reps see which steps the buyer replayed before picking up the phone.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="nt-frame-row reverse">
            <div class="nt-frame-copy">
                <div class="num">02<span class="slash">/</span><span class="lbl">Post-call follow-up</span></div>
                <h3>A follow-up link your champion can <em>actually forward</em> upstairs.</h3>
                <p>Send a NavTour showcase after every call — a branded, self-service experience your champion can share with the CFO, IT, or legal without scheduling another meeting.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Cover slide, company branding, and multi-CTA buttons</li>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Notification when the showcase is re-opened</li>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Gated with a lead form if cold outbound</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="nt-frame-visual">
                <span class="nt-frame-cap">Showcase &middot; post-call</span>
                <div class="nt-frame-img">
                    <img src="/images/shots/showcases.png" alt="Showcase link for post-call follow-up" class="nt-lightbox" />
                </div>
                <div class="anno bl">
                    <div class="lbl">Champion tool</div>
                    <strong>Share upward without a meeting</strong>
                    <p>Champions forward the link. Stakeholders self-serve. Deals progress.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

        <article class="nt-frame-row">
            <div class="nt-frame-copy">
                <div class="num">03<span class="slash">/</span><span class="lbl">Pipeline intel</span></div>
                <h3>Know who&rsquo;s hot before your next <em>pipeline review.</em></h3>
                <p>Step-level analytics and AI intent scoring surface which prospects are re-engaging so reps act on signal, not guesswork — and managers forecast with confidence.</p>
                <ul>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Per-viewer intent score synced to HubSpot / Salesforce</li>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Slack alert when a high-intent lead re-views</li>
                    <li><span class="chk">&#10003;</span>Demo engagement data in every deal record</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="nt-frame-visual">
                <span class="nt-frame-cap">Analytics &middot; intent signals</span>
                <div class="nt-frame-img">
                    <img src="/images/shots/analytics.png" alt="Analytics showing buyer intent signals" class="nt-lightbox" />
                </div>
                <div class="anno tr">
                    <div class="lbl">Signal</div>
                    <strong>Act on engagement, not gut feel</strong>
                    <p>Who replayed which step is more predictive than email open rate.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>
    </div>
</section>

<div class="nt-results" style="padding-top:0">
    <div class="nt-container">
        <div class="nt-stats">
            <div class="nt-stat">
                <div class="lbl">Conversion lift</div>
                <div class="n">2.4<span class="sym">&times;</span></div>
                <p>Demo-to-meeting rate when a pre-call NavTour is sent vs. cold calendar invite.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="nt-stat">
                <div class="lbl">Time saved</div>
                <div class="n">40<span class="sym">%</span></div>
                <p>Reduction in discovery call time when buyers self-qualify before the meeting.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="nt-stat">
                <div class="lbl">Champion forwarding</div>
                <div class="n">73<span class="sym">%</span></div>
                <p>Of showcases sent post-call are forwarded to at least one additional stakeholder.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<NtCTABand Headline="Ship your first pre-call demo this afternoon."
           SubText="Free to start, no credit card. The Chrome extension captures any web app in under 2 minutes."
           PrimaryLabel="Start free &rarr;"
           SecondaryLabel="See all solutions"
           SecondaryHref="/solutions" />
